The paper also discusses the hierarchy of definitions, which could be seen as a combinatorial problem, falling under cs.CC. The characterization of differences in strength using weak instances of the Law of Excluded Middle suggests a connection to proof theory and constructive mathematics, which are covered in cs.DM and cs.LM.
